                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                      As sponsors and challenge setters for <strong class="font-semibold">LincolnHack</strong>, they demonstrate ongoing dedication to growth and innovation in the healthcare technology sector.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                      Visit the <a href="https://www.streets-heaver.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">Streets Heaver website</a> or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/streets-heaver-healthcare-computing/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">LinkedIn</a> for more information.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  

                  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Challenge</h1>
                    
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-700">
                      To follow...
